		"description": {
			"value": "<p><em>Wondrous Item - Uncommon</em></p><p><strong>Action</strong></p><ul><li><p>These pipes have 3 charges and regain 1d3 expended charges daily at dawn. You can take a Action to play them and expend 1 charge to create an eerie, spellbinding tune. Each creature of your choice within 30 feet of you must succeed on a [[/save WIS 15]]{DC 15 Wisdom saving throw} or have the &amp;Reference[Frightened apply=false] condition for 1 minute. A creature that fails the save repeats it at the end of each of its turns, ending the effect on itself on a success. A creature that succeeds on its save is immune to the effect of these pipes for 24 hours.</p></li></ul>",
